<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="till-prep">till <strong><em>prep</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /tɪl/    美 /tɪl/  </p>
<p>[一般不用于句首]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>直到...为止：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We had very good weather this winter, till now. 
今年冬天，直到现在天气都很好。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>在...以前；直到... (才)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I didn’t know about the news till just now.
直到现在我才知道那个消息。</p></div></div>